        </li>
        </ol>
      </p>
    </statement>
  </exercise>

  <exercise>
    <statement>
      <p>
        In each of the following you are given a linear map <m>T</m> and its value on a few specified elements. Find missing values:
      <ol label="(a)">
        <li>
          If <m>T:\Row_2\to \Row_3</m> satisfies <m>T(1,0) = (2,1,-1)</m> and <m>T(0,1) = (1,1,2)</m>, find <m>T(3,-2)</m>;
        </li>
        <li>
